Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.60,0:37:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好\NOkay, Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.24,0:39:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,（法语）大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.35,0:39:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,（缅甸语）你们好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.76,0:39:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,（希伯来语）你好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.87,0:39:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）你好 向大家致敬
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.38,0:39:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,（印尼语）女士们先生们 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.94,0:39:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,（印尼语）再见期待下次再见
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.87,0:39:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,（克丘亚语）用克丘亚语向你们
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.98,0:39:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,（克丘亚语）每一个人问好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.76,0:39:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,（旁遮普语）欢迎你们
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.70,0:39:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,（赫梯语）你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.74,0:39:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,（孟加拉语）你好 愿到处都有和平
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.58,0:39:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）无论你们是谁 你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.17,0:39:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）我们对你们心怀善意
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.15,0:39:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）并带着和平穿梭星际
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.89,0:39:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[左声道 右声道]
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.82,0:39:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,（亚兰语）你好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.39,0:39:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,（荷兰语）向每个人致以诚挚的问候
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.66,0:39:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,（德语）向所有人致以诚挚的问候
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.74,0:39:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌尔都语）愿和平与你们同在
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.88,0:39:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌尔都语）我们代表地球的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.85,0:39:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[（基洛纳区-监视点J3 1990年6月29日）]
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.79,0:39:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌尔都语）欢迎你们
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.67,0:40:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉来晚了\NSorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.34,0:40:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,路上堵死了 我又没法早点走\NTraffic was hell, and I couldn't leave early.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.14,0:40:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 趁还有时间聊聊吧\NLet's just use the time we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.31,0:40:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,今天感觉怎么样 克拉克？\NHow are you today, Clark?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.51,0:40:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你看得我怎么样？\NHow do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.78,0:40:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的 可能有点累吧\NFine. A little tired, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.45,0:40:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我简直糟糕透了\NI look like shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.52,0:40:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我想确认一下\NCan I ask, and there is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.89,0:40:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,放心回答 没什么对错\Nno wrong answer here, you know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.86,0:40:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在是不是受到酒精影响？\NAre you intoxicated right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.56,0:40:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛这么问？\NWhy you say it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.03,0:40:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么问了？\NLike what?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.93,0:40:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我从周五起就没碰过一滴酒\NI haven't had a drink since Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.80,0:40:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没准儿我这副鬼样子就是因为没喝酒\NIt's probably why I look like shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.14,0:40:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我能问你个事吗？ - 请说\N- Can I ask you something? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.37,0:40:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你把人强制关精神病院过吗？\NYou ever 5150'd someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.37,0:40:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[【加州法律5150条：强制将危险精神病人送院观察】]
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.54,0:40:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这么多年确实有过几次 只要情况需要\NA few times over the years, when it was necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.75,0:40:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那...那...那什么样的情况才算需要？\NWh-wha-what makes it necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.25,0:41:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我认为对方有伤人自残的风险\NIf I believe that the person is a danger to themselves or others,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.58,0:41:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,或者无法自理\Nor they're gravely disabled.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.46,0:41:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,行 行 \NOkay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.63,0:41:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...\NUm...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.03,0:41:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我在店里发现了点情况\NI found something in the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.53,0:41:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好 什么情况\NOkay. What did you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.14,0:41:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.81,0:41:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是个地方 我...\NA place. I f...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.51,0:41:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现了个地方\NI found a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.18,0:41:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,地方？\NA place?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.48,0:41:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 感觉...\NYeah. It's like, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.02,0:41:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉店就那样...\NIt's like the store just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.75,0:41:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,往外扩了\Ncontinues, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.09,0:41:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吧...店有墙\NIt's like... you know, like there's a wall
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.99,0:41:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,墙后头居然还是店\Nand on the other side of the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.32,0:41:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没完没了地往外扩\Nthe store just keeps going, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.13,0:41:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就像 就像 像个克隆的 \Nlike-like a... like a copy of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.43,0:41:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我猜入口是用镜子什么的给挡住的\NI-I-I figure they're using mirrors or something
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.20,0:41:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定\Nto hide the entrance, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.10,0:41:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我没听明白\NSorry, I'm not following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.93,0:41:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说找到了个之前没发现的房间？\NIs this a room you didn't know about before?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.07,0:41:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.77,0:41:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就是...就是你一进去后\NOkay, so y-y-you go in and, uh, at first
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.80,0:41:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,看着像个...像个写字楼\Nit just looks like a- like an office building.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.84,0:41:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一个巨大的办公室 你懂吧？\NLike a... like a huge office building, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.81,0:41:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,然后...你 你继续往里走\NAnd then, uh... But then you-you keep going,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.85,0:42:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,接着...接着你就发现\Nand then-then you realize
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.98,0:42:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所...所有东西都不对劲\Nth-th-that none of it makes any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.45,0:42:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢...嗯...想象一下\NIt's-it's like, um... Imagine describing a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.02,0:42:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你给个没见过狗的人形容狗\Nto someone who's never seen one before
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.22,0:42:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,然后让那人把狗画出来\Nand then asking them to draw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.89,0:42:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会画对几个地方\NThey might get some things right, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.89,0:42:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但绝不可能全画对\Nbut there's no way they'd get everything right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.66,0:42:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 诡异的在于细节\NYou know, the devil's in the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.93,0:42:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以远看像只狗\NSo from a distance, you look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.60,0:42:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但凑近一看...\Nyou think you're seeing a dog, but then you look clos--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.03,0:42:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛那样看我？\NWhy are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.87,0:42:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在试着理解\NI'm just trying to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.30,0:42:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,呵\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.14,0:42:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你不像个心理医生 怎么表情都写在脸上\NYou know, for a shrink, you got a terrible poker face.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.68,0:42:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的这些听起来很离奇\NWhat you're saying might sound fantastical,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.81,0:42:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但并不危险\Nbut not dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.68,0:42:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那些办公室里有人吗？\NAre there any people in these offices?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.72,0:42:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,没见过 但我能听到\NNot that I've seen. You know, I hear, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.99,0:42:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,听到脚步声 而且...而且我一转眼\NThere's footsteps, an-an-and stuff gets moved around
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.83,0:42:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,东西就被挪了位置\Nwhen I'm not looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.93,0:42:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这听起来很离谱 但你得明白\NI know how this sounds, but you've got to understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.40,0:42:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那地方太大了\Nit's massive in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.03,0:42:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,简直像纽约地铁那么大 懂吧\NLike New-York's-subway-system massive, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.23,0:42:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没准儿里面有好几百人\NFor all I know, there's hundreds of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.77,0:42:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是没看到\NI just haven't seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.24,0:43:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,看\NLook.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.61,0:43:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 这就像个...\NYou see? It's like a...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.21,0:43:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就像个迷宫\NIt's like a maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.35,0:43:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,根本没尽头\NIt just goes on and on and on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.68,0:43:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我有时候真怕自己会迷路\NSometimes I'm scared I'll get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.62,0:43:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那为什么除了你 没人发现这地方？\NWhy do you think no one else has found this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.59,0:43:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我哪知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.96,0:43:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但入口在负一层\NThe entrance is on the subfloor,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.06,0:43:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,所以整个结构\Nso the whole structure is
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.06,0:43:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,估计都在地下 懂吧\Nprobably underground, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.10,0:43:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,地图上根本没这个地方\NIt's not on any city maps.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.96,0:43:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,入口根本看不出来 谁会想到去找？\NThe entrances are hidden, so who'd think to look?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.80,0:43:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我没说不信你...\NI'm not saying I don't believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.90,0:43:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 你跟我说\Nbut you told me yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.77,0:43:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你周五就开始戒酒了\Nyou haven't had a drink since Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.64,0:43:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这会不会导致幻.... - 行了\N- Do you think there is a-- - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.38,0:43:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克拉克 - 停 停\N- Clark-- - No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.05,0:43:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果这是真的... - 行 我懂了 多谢您啊\N- If this is true-- - Yeah, I get it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.55,0:43:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我迟早会带着证据回来\NYou know, I'm gonna come back here with proof
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.12,0:43:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候你得给我好好道歉\Nand you're gonna owe me a serious fucking apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.67,0:44:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,小凯\NKat!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.01,0:44:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,谁呀 来了 来了\NJesus, goddamn, I'm coming! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.62,0:44:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 - 克船长？\N- Hey. - Cap'n Clark?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.52,0:44:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 额... - 等等 等等 小凯 快来\N- Um... - Wait, wait, wait, wait. Kat?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.62,0:44:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我来了 - 快点\N- I'm coming. - Kat!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.99,0:44:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 我来了\NOkay, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.42,0:44:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是这样的... - 搞什么鬼\N- Look-- -What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.09,0:44:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 那个...\NYeah, I'm sorry, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.69,0:45:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你们明天有空吗？\NWhat are you guys doing tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.33,0:45:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢？\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.09,0:45:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我给钱 算加班 顶多两个小时 很快的\NI'll pay you. Two hours. Overtime. Tops.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.03,0:45:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,行 给钱干什么？\NOkay, pay us for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.87,0:45:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,做调研\NResearch.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.84,0:45:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,摄像机还在你们那儿吧？\NYou got the camera, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.17,0:45:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能...能再帮我拍点东西吗？\NYou can-you can borrow it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.78,0:45:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,行不行？\NRight?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.05,0:45:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 开始拍了\NOkay, we are rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.75,0:45:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿摆了些东西\NWe got, um, some shit over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.01,0:45:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[车停]
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.82,0:45:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,还有停车牌\NWe got some stop signs
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.69,0:45:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 呃 绳子\Nand, uh... a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.13,0:45:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,拿绳子干嘛？\NWhat's the rope for?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.39,0:45:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,装备\NSupplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.93,0:45:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,呵呵 看来咱们要被他绑了\NOh, great, he's gonna tie us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.07,0:45:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我绑 是要给自己绑好\NNo, we're gonna tie ourselves up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.13,0:45:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,唔 挺重口味的\NHmm. Kinky.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.54,0:45:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼\NWhat the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.94,0:45:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 你还没说清楚\NUh, you still haven't told us
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.10,0:45:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来这儿干嘛？\Nwhat we're doing here, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.14,0:45:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了 做调研\NI did tell you. Research.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.41,0:45:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是调研装备\NThese are supplies, and we're using them for research.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.28,0:45:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没那么难理解吧\NIt's not that hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.71,0:45:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,行 研究什么？\NOkay, research for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.82,0:45:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你得具体点 老哥\NY-you gotta be more specific, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.15,0:46:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我要进门了\NI'm gonna go through the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.49,0:46:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什么门？\NWhat door?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.02,0:46:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是门\NThat's the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.19,0:46:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我在另一边也贴了框\NI taped an outline on the other side, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.03,0:46:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,以防咱们找不到\Njust to help us find our way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.46,0:46:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿博？ - 怎么了？\N- Bobby? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.83,0:46:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我知道这很离谱 但得听我的\NLook, I know it sounds crazy, but follow my lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.14,0:46:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,懂吗？\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.84,0:46:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我想在天亮前赶回来\NI want to be back before sunup.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.77,0:46:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,老哥 现在才晚上九点 你说什么...\NDude, it's like 9 p.m. What the fuck are you talk--
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.21,0:46:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么情况 克拉克 - 卧槽\N- What the fuck! Clark?! - What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.48,0:46:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么做到的？ - 老哥 你...\N- How did you do that? - Dude, did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.25,0:46:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看到了吧？他怎么会...呃...\NDid you fucking see that?! H-how did he, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.72,0:46:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在这儿 快进来看看\NI'm right here. Come see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.38,0:46:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼 你居然真的...\NWhat the fuck? D-did you just fucking...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.15,0:46:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？怎么会...\NWhat? How the f...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.22,0:46:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛呢？阿博 快住手\NBobby, stop. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.86,0:46:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我去 - 克拉克 你在哪儿？\N- What the fuck?! - Clark, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.36,0:46:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 你...你看到了没？\NHa! Hey, did you... did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.23,0:46:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他钻哪去了？ - 看到了 阿博 我看到了\N- Where the fuck did he go? - Yes, Bobby, I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.46,0:46:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我去 搞什...\NOh! Where the f--
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.26,0:46:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,踏进来就行 没事的\NJust step through the door, you'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.23,0:46:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,疯了吧 你得先解释清楚\NWhat?! No! Tell us what is going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.24,0:46:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,管他呢 直接...\NYou know what, just...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.74,0:46:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不 阿博 别进去 阿博 快停下 你要干什么？\NNo, Bobby, wait! Bobby! Wait, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.44,0:46:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博\NBobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.17,0:46:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我去啊\NWhat the fuck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.64,0:47:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,老哥\NDude!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.04,0:47:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,老哥 这怎么可能？\NDude, how is this possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.85,0:47:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿博 克拉克 - 行...\N- Bobby! Clark! - Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.12,0:47:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在哪？里面到底是什么地方？\NWhere are you? What the fuck is back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.72,0:47:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没事没事 小凯 没事的\NNo, no, no, Kat, it's good, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.09,0:47:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧进来看看\NJ-just, you gotta come see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.32,0:47:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说...对 你看...\NI mean... Right, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.33,0:47:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你看这 呃...\NYou see, it's, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.00,0:47:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没问题 - 克拉克 这是什么地方？\N- It's fine. - Clark, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.26,0:47:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们在哪？ - 哦\N- Where are we? - Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.06,0:47:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我也正想弄明白呢\NThat's what I'm trying to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.17,0:47:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这...这是谁的东西？\NWhose, um... Whose shit is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.24,0:47:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是你...是你店里的吗？\NIs it-is it... is it part of your store?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.10,0:47:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真有主的话\NIf it belongs to someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.64,0:47:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我还没碰到那个人 - 好吧\N- I haven't met them yet. - Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.41,0:47:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,自从发现这地方 我每晚都来\NI've been in here every night since I found the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.28,0:47:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但也就看了个冰山一角\Nand I still barely scratched the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.18,0:47:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,走 我带你们看看\NCome on. I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.55,0:47:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,越往后越有意思\NIt only gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.25,0:47:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真扯... - 嘿 嘿\N- What the fuck... - Hey. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.55,0:47:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得他给我们下药了吧？\NYou don't think he, like, dosed us or something, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.32,0:47:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？没那回事 咱们没磕药\NWhat? No, no, no. We're not on drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.39,0:47:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我嗨了 肯定能感觉到\NI think I'd be able to tell if I was high.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.49,0:47:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在就嗨着呢\NYou are high!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.59,0:47:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,抽草不算\NPot doesn't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.93,0:47:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,所以...这就像...\NSo, um, it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.97,0:47:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,像个空办公区？\Nwhat, like an empty office building?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.77,0:47:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在这儿？算是吧 但这地方简直像是\NIn here? Sure. But it's like it was made
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.20,0:48:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一帮嗑嗨了的建筑工盖出来的\Nby a bunch of construction workers on acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.14,0:48:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,居然还搞了个泳池\NThere's even a pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.74,0:48:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有泳池？\NThere's a pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.21,0:48:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 算是吧\NYeah. I mean, kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.11,0:48:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,快跟上\NKeep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.45,0:48:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,“车停”什么鬼？\N"Pots." What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.62,0:48:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不 那是我上次走的路\NYeah, no, no, that's the way I went last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.56,0:48:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,当时我想找个楼梯下去什么的\NYeah, when I was looking for a staircase down or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.66,0:48:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,结果只发现了个...\NOnly thing I found so far is basically more of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.53,0:48:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好的...\NOkay...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.37,0:48:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 其实就是个斜坡\NI don't know, it's like a ramp, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.77,0:48:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这儿 呃...前面\NIt's, uh... It's up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.01,0:48:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就到了\NWe'll be at it in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.14,0:48:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.08,0:48:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这下面总共有多少层？\NHow many floors does it go down?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.38,0:48:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这不能用楼层来...\NIs this not technically...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.95,0:48:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 开始拍了吗？\NOkay. All right, you filming?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.69,0:48:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拍了  - 行\N- Yeah. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.35,0:48:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么非得让阿博下去？\NI don't see why Bobby has to be the one to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.22,0:48:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想去 - 摄像机在他手上\N- I want to. - He's the one with the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.79,0:48:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,相机又没长在他身上\NWell, it's not like it's attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.16,0:48:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,它挂在我学生证上的\NYeah, well, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.73,0:48:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就算长在身上了\Nto my student ID, yeah, it kinda is.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.66,0:48:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要是觉得不对劲 就拽一下 我把你拉上来 明白吧？\NAny trouble, just give a tug, and I'll pull you up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.50,0:49:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不对劲？克拉克 下面有什么不对劲？\NTrouble? Clark, what fucking trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.03,0:49:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有事的\NThere's not going to be any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.30,0:49:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝 宝贝 没事\NBabe, babe, babe, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.64,0:49:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别下... - 真的没事 我没问题\N- No, hey-- - It's good. I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.10,0:49:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 你不用下去\NBaby, you don't have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.80,0:49:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 我就是想看看下面有什么\NNo, it's cool. I-I just want to see what's down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.51,0:49:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不好奇吗？ - 简直是疯了\N- Are you not curious? - This is stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.81,0:49:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能走多远就走多远 - 没事 你看 你看\N- Just go as far as you can. - No, look, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.54,0:49:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,其实不用绳子也能走下去\NYou can basically walk down without a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.21,0:49:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么 一点也不陡\NIt's fine, and it's not even steep.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.45,0:49:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,行吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.21,0:49:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好 但有一件事\NOkay, just don't... just one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.92,0:49:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,万一我回不来 记得告诉我妈我爱她哦\NIf I don't come back, you'll tell my mom I love her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.22,0:49:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 行 - 那么 走吧\N- Okay. - All right, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.79,0:49:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好 慢慢来\NAll right, just take it slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.39,0:49:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,行\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.06,0:49:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 实际上还挺陡的\NOh, it is actually kind of steep.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.46,0:49:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没事吧？ - 没事\N- You good? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.20,0:49:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拉紧点 别把我摔了 - 放心\N- Just, uh... try not to drop me. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.14,0:49:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,需要放绳子告诉我\NTell me how much you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.44,0:49:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,喔...慢点\NWhoa... Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.38,0:49:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么...喔 喔 喔 操 啊\NWhat the... Whoa! Whoa! Whoa! Fuck! Aah...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.75,0:49:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你上面怎么拉的绳子？\NWhat the fuck are you guys doing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.35,0:49:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起\NSorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.16,0:49:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,绳子卡在床腿上了\NIt was stuck around the leg of the bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.76,0:50:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧？ - 行 没事\N- Are you okay? - Yeah. Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.06,0:50:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真是绝了\NJesus fucking Christ...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.39,0:50:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,继续放绳子\NJust keep letting me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.23,0:50:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 来了\NAll right. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.05,0:50:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我下来了\NOkay, I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.89,0:50:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,看到什么没？\NSee anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.22,0:50:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...\NUgh...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.29,0:50:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 就是...\NUh, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.76,0:50:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一堆脏衣服和垃圾\NIt's a bunch of laundry and shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.60,0:50:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思？衣服？\NWhat do you mean? Clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.67,0:50:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,对 这下面真是臭死了\NYeah, it just fucking stinks down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.20,0:50:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么吗？\NSee anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.57,0:50:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有 呃...给我点时间\NYeah, just, uh... Just give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.30,0:50:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.94,0:50:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\NOh, god...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.75,0:51:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[结束南非种族隔离]
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.69,0:51:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼？\NWhat the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.09,0:51:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[【结束南非种族隔离：是80年代盛行的现实世界口号】]
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.13,0:51:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博？\NBobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.63,0:51:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.46,0:51:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就想确认下你没事\NJust checking that you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.23,0:51:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我没事 只是 呃...\NYeah, I'm fine. Just, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.04,0:51:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.17,0:51:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.11,0:51:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.42,0:51:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼？\NWhat the fuck...?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.03,0:51:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博？快上来\NBobby? Come back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.43,0:51:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我心里发毛\NI don't like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.30,0:51:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 呃...再多放点绳子\NHey! Uh... Let some more line out!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.73,0:51:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 已经到头了\NI can't! It's as far as it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.77,0:51:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\NFuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.11,0:52:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我操 快拉我上去\NFuck! Pull me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.31,0:52:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博 怎么了？\NBobby! What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.85,0:52:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 操 - 你看到了什么？\N- Fuck! - What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.68,0:52:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,磨蹭什么 快把他拉上来\NWhat the fuck is it? Pull him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.02,0:52:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我在拉啊 我的天 - 操\N- I am! Jesus Christ! -Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.22,0:52:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,拉快点\NPull harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.52,0:52:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快拉 老哥 搞什么鬼\NPull, man! What the fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.86,0:52:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,绳子绕到我脚上了\NIt's getting caught on my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.52,0:52:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 绳子绕到我脚上了 - 快点使劲拉\N- I can't pull-- - Fucking pull harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.33,0:52:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 快点拉\NClark, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.83,0:52:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,快到了 快到了 宝贝 坚持住\NAlmost here! Almost here, babe, just a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.77,0:52:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快把他拉上来 - 你看到了什么？\N- Pull him up! - What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.93,0:52:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,下...下面有人\NThere's, uh, there's someone down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.84,0:52:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你安全了...什么？- 操\N- We've got you. What? - Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.37,0:52:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,慢点说 深呼吸 宝贝 没事了\NSlow down, just breathe. Baby, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.01,0:52:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,快把这破玩意儿给我解开 操 真是够了\NJust get this shit off me, man. Fuck. Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.77,0:52:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没事了 没事了 - 你看到了什么？\N-I t's okay. It's okay. - What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.08,0:52:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来 深呼吸 - 这打的什么破结？\N- Here. Hey, deep breath. - What kind of knot is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.24,0:52:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,深呼吸...\NDeep breath--
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.58,0:52:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 卧槽？！ - 哎 哎 哎\N- What the fuck?! - Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.11,0:52:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快救命 克拉克 - 抓紧我\N- Help us! Clark! - Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.98,0:52:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来了 来了 来了 - 救人啊 你个混蛋\N- Okay, okay, okay! - Help, you fucking asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.65,0:52:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让我解 - 快给我解开 老哥\N- Let me get it! - Untie me, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.72,0:52:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 你特么在磨蹭什么？\NWhat the hell are you doing, Clark?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.22,0:52:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我解不开 - 快点 克拉克\N- I can't! - Hurry, Clark!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.42,0:52:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我在弄了 我在弄了 - 操！\N- I'm trying, I'm trying! - FUCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.76,0:52:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,别松手 别松手\NDon't let go! Don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.69,0:52:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 坚持住 - 操 千万别放手\N- Hold on! - Fuck! Don't let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.59,0:52:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 千万别放手 - 我去拿...\N- Don't let me go! - Let me get at--
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.66,0:52:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博！\NBOBBY!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.23,0:52:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不 小凯 不\NNO! KAT, NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.63,0:52:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博\NBobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.73,0:52:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博！\NBOBBY!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.40,0:52:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博\NBobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.57,0:52:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事 我们得...克拉克\NWhat are we doing? We need to... Clark!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.51,0:53:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博 别 别 别\NBobby! No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.35,0:53:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别 小凯 小凯\NOw... KAT! Kat...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.35,0:53:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博\NBobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.19,0:53:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博 不\NBobby! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.62,0:53:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博 不\NBobby! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.29,0:53:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,小凯\NKat!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.63,0:53:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 该死\NOh, fuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.13,0:53:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不 不 不 不 不 不\NOh, no, no, no, no, no! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.78,0:54:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,小凯？\NKat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.85,0:54:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,小凯？\NKat?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.54,0:55:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗？\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.71,0:55:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,别过来 滚开\NStay back! Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.64,0:56:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 克拉克 我在在这...\NClark? CLARK! I'm here...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.15,0:57:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这 那东西要回来了\NI'm here! It's gonna come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.81,0:57:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,快让我进去 克拉克 求你让我进去\NPlease, Clark, please let me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.62,0:57:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 小凯？ - 让我进去\N- Kat? - Let me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.49,0:57:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你...你在在哪？\NWh-wh-where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.22,0:57:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得赶紧走 克拉克 没时间了\NWe have to go now, Clark! We have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.09,0:57:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那东西要回来了 它会找到我的\NIt's gonna come back, it's gonna find me!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.13,0:57:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,小凯 小凯？额...等等 我没搞明白 你到底在哪？\NKat! Kat? Uh... Wait, I don't understand. Wh-where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.26,0:57:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的 快让我进去\NPlease, let me the fuck in!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.07,0:57:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但这...这是堵墙啊\NBut it's a... it's-it's a wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.43,0:57:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能看到我？\NHow can-how can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.64,0:57:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我在玻璃的另一边\NI'm on the other side of the glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.30,0:57:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么看得见...？ - 你怎么看不见我？\N- How can you see...? - How can you not see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.37,0:57:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,什么玻璃？你在说什么鬼话？\NWhat glass?! What the fuck are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.98,0:57:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你在...在说什...？\NWh-what are you talk--
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.11,0:57:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你那边能看到什么吗？\NOkay, can you see anything on your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.48,0:57:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有门把手吗 还是有门？有没有入口之类的东西？\NCan you see a handle, a door? Is there a hatch, anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.22,0:57:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 没有 没有...\NNo, no, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.09,0:57:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...好吧 让我想想办法 好吗？等一下\NUh... Okay. Let me figure this out, okay? Just hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.09,0:57:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住 行吗？只是...\NHold on, okay? It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.16,0:57:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克拉克？ - 别急 别急 让我试...\N- Clark? - No, no, just let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.10,0:57:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克拉克 - 别急\N- Clark! - Just hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.73,0:57:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我找找看 - 克拉克\N- Let me figure this out! - CLARK!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.20,0:57:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别催我 我在想办法 - 克拉克 快跑\N- Let me figure this out... - Clark! Clark!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.30,0:57:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 它就在你身后\NClark, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.68,0:58:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[诺拉·克莱...\N氯丙...]
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.36,0:58:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[【氯丙嗪：抗精神病药物】]
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.78,0:59:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽 住手\NMary!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.23,0:59:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽\NMary...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.49,0:59:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗？\Nwhat were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.26,0:59:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过绝对 绝对\NI never, ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.20,0:59:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不能出门\Never said you could go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.17,0:59:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不行\NIt's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.81,0:59:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,外面到处都是\NThey're all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.95,1:01:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,您拨打的是玛丽·克莱因医生的电话\NHi, you've reached Dr. Mary Klein.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.05,1:01:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我目前不便接听\NI'm not able to answer the call,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.15,1:01:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,请留言\Nso please leave a message,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.09,1:01:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽快给您回电\Nand I'll get back to you as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.53,1:01:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽...\NMary...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.67,1:01:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我打开那扇窗了\NI opened the window.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.94,1:01:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再回来了\NI won't be coming back.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.93,1:02:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[克船长的家具百宝库]
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.18,1:02:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,“...求你了”\N"...Please!"
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.62,1:02:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,“救救我们”\N"Save us!"
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.79,1:02:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[（1983年 异相研究所获得120万美元联邦资助开发下一代核磁共振设备）]
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.46,1:02:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,“好 我照作”\N"All right! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.69,1:02:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,“我会救你们 我会照作”\NI'll save you! I will do it!"
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.37,1:02:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,“梦翠儿！”\N"Moon Child!"
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.22,1:02:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[电影《大魔域》1984：讲述一个男孩通过想象力重建世界的奇幻故事]
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.51,1:02:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道你手之前碰过什么\NI don't know where that hand's been.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.76,1:02:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[【《大魔域》英文片名：直译为“永不结束的故事”】]
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.15,1:02:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,“哟 伙计们 瞧瞧这儿啊！”\N"Well, ahoy there, mateys!"
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.12,1:02:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,“按照这藏宝图”\N"Now, according to me map,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.55,1:02:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,“咱们现在已经登上了这片宝地”\N"we've landed on the crystal shores of a bountiful land,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.19,1:02:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,“这里的折扣简直是在倒贴啊！”\N"a land filled with great deals."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.72,1:02:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[（全市最低价）]
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.09,1:02:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,“你也赶紧赶紧抛锚靠岸！”\N"So drop your anchors and come on down
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.33,1:02:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,“快来克船长的家具百宝库！”\N"to Cap'n Clark's Ottoman Empire."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.13,1:02:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,“潜入这场顶级家具海洋吧”\N"Get lost in an endless sea
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.77,1:02:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,“桌椅沙发 卧室全套 样样齐全！”\N"of quality tables, chairs, couches, and bedroom sets."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.44,1:03:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,“想给小海盗配上下铺？”\N"Need bed bunks for the scallywagses quarters?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.04,1:03:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,“来这儿就对了！”\N"W've got it all!"
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.21,1:03:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,“价格低到...”\N"And at prices so low
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.38,1:03:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,“你都觉得在抢钱啊！”\N"you'll think that yo're robbing me!"
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.64,1:03:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗？\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.89,1:03:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[大促销 大降价]
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.49,1:03:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗？\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.36,1:04:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[大促销 大降价]
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.46,1:03:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克？\NClark?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.15,1:04:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[无需信用卡]
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.98,1:04:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 你在哪儿？\NClark, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.73,1:04:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[楼下更精彩]
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.02,1:04:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克？\NClark?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.03,1:05:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[车停]
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.28,1:05:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[家具店 和 入口]
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.13,1:07:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克？\NClark?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.38,1:09:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[（平面图又变了 屋顶不对 屋顶绝对不对 这图纸是谁签的名？但这笔迹 像我的）]
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.86,1:09:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[（管他的什么超自然 理智点吧）]
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.89,1:09:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[（此刻和此地是相通的）]
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.16,1:10:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克？\NClark?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.76,1:10:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你总算发现了\NYou found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.64,1:10:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么躲起来？\NWhy are you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.61,1:10:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你太吵了\NYou were being too loud.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.16,1:11:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在哪？\NWhere are we?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.83,1:11:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这里...\NIt's...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.60,1:11:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是所有存在过的地方\N...every place that ever was.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.54,1:11:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这儿多久了？\NHow long have you been here?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.58,1:11:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么声音？\NWhat was that?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.76,1:11:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,别紧张\NStay calm.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.90,1:11:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没别人\NIt's only me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.87,1:11:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你是了解我的\NYou know me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.80,1:12:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.60,1:12:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,都是为了你好\NThis is for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.93,1:14:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在现实生活中\NAs you walk through life,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.46,1:14:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,缺乏引导的心灵 总会走入死循环 养成固有的习惯\Nthe untrained mind accumulates loops, habits...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.17,1:14:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,总是重蹈覆辙\N...behaviors that keep you drifting in circles,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.78,1:14:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,陷入相同的问题\Ncreating the same problems,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.15,1:14:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,总是用同样的办法\Nreaching for the same solutions
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.78,1:14:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,一遍又一遍\Nover and over again.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.49,1:15:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟神经通路就爱走阻力最小的路径\NStill, it's the neural pathway of least resistance.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.00,1:15:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这条路径是我自己铺的\NThe one I made.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.83,1:15:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候\NThe one that kept me safe...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.80,1:15:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这套防线保护了我\Nwhen I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.14,1:15:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你看...\NYou know...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.01,1:15:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我学会了抢在被伤害之前 把别人推开\NI learned to push people away before they could hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.34,1:15:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,而现在 我都成年了\NAnd, now, as an adult,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.18,1:15:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,还是留在原地\NI'm still stuck right where I started.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.02,1:15:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一个人\NAlone.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.33,1:15:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\NWhat is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.10,1:15:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真是一团糟 对吧？\NIt's a real mess. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.70,1:15:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克...\NClark...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.57,1:15:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来帮你...\N...let me help you...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.24,1:15:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在你做出无法挽回的事之前\Nbefore you do anything you can't take back.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.81,1:15:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我的问题\NAnswer the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.51,1:15:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 真是一团糟\NYes, it's a real mess.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.85,1:15:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但从某种角度看 也很美\NBut also beautiful in a way.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.45,1:15:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吗？\NNo?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.73,1:16:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人是谁？\NWho are these people?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.00,1:16:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方造了他们\NThis place builds them.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.83,1:16:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 其实更像是在记得他们\NOh, actually, more like it remembers them.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.30,1:16:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只不过记得越多\NAnd the more times it remembers something,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.61,1:16:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就越走样\Nthe less it does.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.04,1:16:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这个在外面是个穿条纹衫的家伙\NSomewhere out there is a guy in a striped shirt,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.48,1:16:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但在这儿...\Nbut, in here, he's...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.72,1:16:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他被记成了这样\Nremembered.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.78,1:16:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有点走样\NJust slightly wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.89,1:16:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这个在外面是个...\NSomewhere out there is a man
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.92,1:16:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,坐轮椅的家伙 带了盏灯\Nin a wheelchair, and a lamp.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.47,1:16:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢说 这里就是这么回事\NI'm pretty sure that's how you get all of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.77,1:16:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所有这些地方啊\NYou know, all these places
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.67,1:16:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,房间和建筑啊\Nand rooms and buildings
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.61,1:17:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,全都记岔了\Nmisremembering themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.05,1:17:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克...\NClark...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.85,1:17:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们好好谈谈吧\Nlet's talk this through.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.33,1:17:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,换个角度看...\NIn some ways...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.85,1:17:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们甚至比原件更好\Nthey're an improvement on the originals.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.89,1:17:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,比如...\NFor starters,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.16,1:17:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有任何感觉\Nthey can't feel anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.30,1:17:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,想象一下 那样得有多自在啊\NCan you imagine how good that must feel?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.58,1:17:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说...\NI mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.61,1:17:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没念头 没痛苦 没自我 也没恐惧\N...there's no thoughts or pain, no ego, no fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.88,1:17:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,纯粹就是...\NThey simply...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.52,1:17:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在那儿\Nexist.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.99,1:17:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就像...就像家具一样\NLike... like furniture!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.06,1:17:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看这儿 最绝的来了\NLook at this. The best part.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.54,1:17:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他们能吃\NYou can eat them!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.78,1:18:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的 呃...\NThat's my, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.62,1:18:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,助理\Nassistant manager.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.95,1:18:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我想帮她 但她就是...\NI tried to help her, but she just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.29,1:18:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克\NClark!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.62,1:18:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我解开 我们可以聊聊\NIf you untie me, we can talk this through,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.79,1:18:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,让你心里好受点\Nget you feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.46,1:18:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 就算解开了\NYeah, well, what if I did untie you?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.03,1:18:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎样？\NYou know, what then?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.93,1:19:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你顶多像个\NYou'd run around here
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.50,1:19:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没头苍蝇一样到处乱窜\Nlike a chicken with its head cut off,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.83,1:19:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,找你的出口\Nlooking for a way out.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.71,1:19:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但你最后还是得回到这儿\NBut you'd end up in the same place you are now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.14,1:19:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就跟你爱说的那套路径理论一样\NLike the path thing you're always talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.78,1:19:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克\NClark!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.31,1:19:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我是真的想帮你 只要告诉我你想要什么\NI just want to help you. Just tell me what you need.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.12,1:19:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我...我一定照做\NI'll-I'll-I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.45,1:19:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？\NYeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.69,1:19:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 是的 拜托了\NYeah. Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.92,1:19:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,行\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.03,1:19:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我想听你亲口说\NWell, I want you to tell me
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.63,1:19:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我没做错任何事\Nthat I didn't do anything wrong, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.30,1:19:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是你之前对我看走眼了\Nthat-that you were wrong about me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.20,1:19:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是我看走眼了 我错\NI was wrong about you! I was.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.14,1:19:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我真的看错你了 - 不 不 不要这样\N- I was wrong about you. - No, no, not-not like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.21,1:19:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,别 别这么快 好吗？\NNot... not so fast, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.08,1:19:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 我想...我想先定个场景\NI mean, I wanna... I want to set the scene first!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.75,1:19:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们从...\NLet's start, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.05,1:19:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 从那晚开始\Nwell, the night that, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.45,1:19:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我被撵出我自己家的那晚\Nthat I got kicked out of my own house.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.69,1:19:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？\NYeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.06,1:20:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那天 嗯...很晚了\NIt was, um... It was late.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.00,1:20:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,屋里很暗\NA lot darker.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.43,1:20:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.84,1:20:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,关下灯\NLights, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.92,1:20:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,之前跟她试过 她根不会动\NI tried this exercise with her before.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.18,1:20:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,结果都一样\NIt doesn't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.85,1:20:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,行\NFine!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.36,1:20:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己来\NI'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.02,1:20:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟 这终究还是我的房子\NIt's still my house after all.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.63,1:20:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.23,1:20:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 这样才对\NThank you. Much better.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.94,1:20:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不过...\NBut there's...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.84,1:20:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,还是...\Nstill...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.07,1:20:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有点走样\Nsomething off.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.16,1:21:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 求你..\NClark, please...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.36,1:21:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不 拜托 不要 不要...\NNo, please, don't, don't...!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.08,1:22:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.18,1:22:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我...\NI'm sorry, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.09,1:22:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,把杯子打碎了 还把你吵醒了\Nbroke the glass and woke you up.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.73,1:22:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你睡得早\NI know how you like to sleep early.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.07,1:22:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我在店里忙太久了\NI was at the store late.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.70,1:22:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,忘了时间\NI guess I lost track of the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.51,1:22:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,当时在对账\NI was checking inventory.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.61,1:22:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,然后...\NBut...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.48,1:22:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,顺路喝了点啤酒\NI stopped off for a few beers.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.41,1:22:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克拉克 - 芭芭拉\N- Clark-- - Barbara!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.78,1:22:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时在对账\NI was checking inventory.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.72,1:22:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,然后顺路喝了点啤酒\NThen I stopped off for a few beers.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.66,1:22:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一点...一点是多少？\NDefi-define a few.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.43,1:22:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我想喝多少就喝多少\NAs many as I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.50,1:22:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这房子是我的\NBecause this is my house.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.34,1:22:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,房贷是我在还\NI pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.64,1:23:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的钱都是我出的 你上学是我供\NI pay for everything. I pay for you to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.24,1:23:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,休学是我供\NI pay for your time off school!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.68,1:23:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,连住这儿都是我供的\NI pay for the roof over your head!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.18,1:23:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要孩子 对吧？\NYou want kids, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.18,1:23:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,养孩子得花钱\NWell, that takes money.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.79,1:23:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,总得有人去挣钱\NSo someone has to work around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.12,1:23:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过了这儿得有人干活\NI said someone has
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.72,1:23:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不能在那儿当个懒猪混吃等死\Nto get off her fat ass and work around here!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.73,1:23:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你没考上建筑师 并不代表...\NJust because you didn't get to be an architect don--
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.56,1:23:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,老子就是建筑师\NI am a fucking architect.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.10,1:23:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我成天得在那破店里卖这些玩意儿\NI'm just stuck selling shit furniture because someone
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.53,1:23:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为某个懒猪在家混吃等死 根本不肯出力！\Nwon't get off her fat fucking ass and help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.44,1:23:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我才不是你老婆 - 别出戏\N- I'm not your wife! - Stay in character.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.51,1:23:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,继续演\NStay in character!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.34,1:23:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我压根就没见过她 - 继续演你的角色\N-I've never even met her! -STAY IN CHARACTER!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.11,1:23:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,滚你妈的蛋\NFUCK YOU!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.68,1:23:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么？\NWhat did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.58,1:23:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道为什么你老婆甩了你吗？\NYou wanna know the real reason your wife left you?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.35,1:23:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不是因为酗酒\NIt wasn't the drinking,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.55,1:23:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不是半夜烂醉回家 甚至不是你的坏脾气\Nor the stumbling home at all hours, or the rage.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.76,1:23:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为你是个巨婴\NIt was the whining!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.76,1:23:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你这辈子没一件事是你的错 对吧？\NNothing's ever your fault, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.33,1:23:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,喝多了 赖工作\NYou drink too much? Blame your job.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.40,1:24:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,恨工作 赖世界\NYou hate your job? Blame the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.27,1:24:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,被撵出家门\NYou get kicked out of the house?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.27,1:24:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,赖老婆\NBlame your wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.07,1:24:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你攻击我 绑架我\NYou attack me and tie me up?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.34,1:24:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,居然还赖在脑子上？\NBlame your brain!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.31,1:24:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你这颗烂脑子 就是你本人 废物\NYou are your fucking brain, you dipshit!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.25,1:24:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 所以 全都是我的错？ - 是啊\N- You're saying it's my fault? - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.55,1:24:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但你肯定又要赖你的脑回路 对吧？\NBut it's just the way you're wired, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.58,1:24:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,对不对\NISN'T IT?!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.43,1:24:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那我怎么才能停下来？\NHow do I stop doing that?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.26,1:24:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,实话实说 我一丁点的招都没有了\NHonestly, I have no fucking idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.40,1:24:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮不了你 克拉克\NI can't help you, Clark.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.50,1:24:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,能试的我都试了\NAs much as I tried.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.54,1:24:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这根本不是我能左右的\NIt's just not up to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.95,1:24:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我谁也救不了\NI can't save anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.26,1:25:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗...\NYou know...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.53,1:25:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我其实不想改\NI don't think I want to change.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.10,1:25:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那就别改\NThen don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.81,1:25:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这里\NI like it in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.68,1:25:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这么久以来\NFor the first time in a long time,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.42,1:25:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次觉得...\NI feel like I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.69,1:25:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我终于回到了该在的地方\Nlike I'm right where I'm supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.19,1:25:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那就留下吧\NThen stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.60,1:25:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么待着\NRight where you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.90,1:25:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但你得放我走\NBut let me go.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.17,1:26:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.44,1:26:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,道什么歉？\NAbout what?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.44,1:26:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你来这儿干什么？\NWhat are you doing in here?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.51,1:27:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这是玛丽\NThis is Mary.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.58,1:27:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,她是咱们的心理治疗师\NShe's our therapist.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.58,1:27:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,她正要离开\NShe was just leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.39,1:27:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不\NNo, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.69,1:27:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用担心\NYou don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.30,1:27:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她说咱们不需要改变\NShe says we don't need to change.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.51,1:27:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.58,1:27:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是咱们的脑回路\NIt's just the way we're wired.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.10,1:31:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[楼下更精彩]
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.58,1:31:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[等待翻译]\NMusulayo mutya abantu bensi eno
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.08,1:31:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[等待翻译]\Nmukama abawe emirembe bulijo.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.68,1:31:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[大促销 大降价]
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.54,1:31:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[等待翻译]\NÜdözletet ülünk magyar...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.17,1:31:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不\NNo...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.85,1:31:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[出口]
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.33,1:32:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[大促销 大降价]
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.66,1:32:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[等待翻译]\NHello from the children of Planet Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.24,1:32:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[大促销 大降价]
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.41,1:32:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[等待翻译]\NPaz e felicidade a todos.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.99,1:32:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[等待翻译]\NZdrávstvuyte! Privétstvuyu Vas!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.01,1:33:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[等待翻译]\NBonjour tout le monde.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.18,1:35:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.05,1:35:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这女人是谁？\NWho the fuck is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.15,1:35:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？\NWho is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.69,1:35:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.62,1:35:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,海盗呢？还在附近吗？\NWhat about the pirate? Can you still see the pirate?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.76,1:35:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人呢？他们还在后撤吗？\NAnd the other guys? Still going out the back?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.65,1:36:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[等待翻译]\NMusulayo mutya abantu bensi eno
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.76,1:36:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[等待翻译]\Nmukama abawe emirembe bulijo.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.90,1:36:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[等待翻译]\NThài-khong pêng-iú, lín-hó.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.14,1:36:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[等待翻译]\NÜdözletet ülünk magyar
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.48,1:37:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[等待翻译]\Nnyelven minden békét szereö lénynek aVilágegyetemen.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.76,1:37:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[等待翻译]\NHello from the children of Planet Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.71,1:38:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 我叫菲尔\NHello, my name is Phil.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.75,1:38:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你是玛丽 对吧？\NAnd you're Mary, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.48,1:38:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我想问你几个问题 主要是...\NUh... I was hoping to ask you a few questions, just for...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.42,1:38:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,为了核实一些细节\Nsome clarification on our end,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.96,1:38:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吧？\Nif that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.37,1:38:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 首先...\NUh, first thing, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.61,1:38:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你能说说 你是怎么...\Ncould you establish how you, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.84,1:38:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,进去的吗？\Ngot in here?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.25,1:38:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我穿过了一家\NI walked through a wall
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.18,1:38:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,家具店地下室的墙\Nin the basement of a furniture store.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.89,1:38:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你看这张照片 是这里吧？\NCan you confirm that this is the location in question?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.43,1:38:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[克船长的家具百宝库]
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.87,1:39:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 你当时是想来购物 还是...\NOkay, good. So you were shopping, or...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.98,1:39:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时在找人\NI was looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.48,1:39:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...\NUm...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.49,1:39:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你找的那个人\Nwere you looking for this man,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.22,1:39:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是他吧？\Nright here?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.70,1:39:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在在哪？\NWhere am I right now?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.00,1:39:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我确认一下行吗？\NCould you just confirm for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.00,1:39:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你要找的人吧？\NIs this man right here the man you were looking for?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.74,1:39:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.30,1:39:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉 你刚才说你叫什么？ - 菲尔\N- Sorry, what was your name? - Phil.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.44,1:39:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 菲尔 告诉我我现在在哪？\NPlease, Phil. Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.61,1:39:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不...\NI'm not...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.42,1:39:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我是做...呃...抱歉 我的...\NI make, um... Sorry, my...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.29,1:39:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的公司 生产...\NOur company, we make...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.63,1:40:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,核磁共振成像仪\NMRI machines.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.83,1:40:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,, 或者...应该说\NOr... I should say, um,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.23,1:40:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们曾经是做核磁共振仪的\Nwe used to make MRI machines.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.10,1:40:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不做了\NNot anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.44,1:40:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那是在我们...\NThat was before we...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.51,1:40:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在我们发现那个.... - 你也去过那里\N- Before we found-- - You've been there.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.58,1:40:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我去过\NYes, I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.32,1:40:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,现在这成了我的工作\NAnd now, it's my job.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.59,1:40:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我每天...每天都进去 试着...\NEvery day, I-I go in there and I just try to f...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.70,1:40:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,试着哪怕能多弄懂一点也好\Ntry to find out ev-even a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.47,1:40:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我在尽全力绘制地图\NI-I map out areas to the best of my ability.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.14,1:40:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽 我越来越坚信\NAnd more and more, I'm convinced
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.44,1:40:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们有生之年\Nthat nothing in our lifetime, Mary,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.61,1:40:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,甚甚至在整个人类记录的历史中\Nn-nothing in-in maybe all of recorded history
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.55,1:40:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么比这个更有分量了\Nmeans more than this.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.59,1:41:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,可我就是没搞明白\NBut I don't understand it. I don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.89,1:41:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我根本说不上来\NI-I can't even describe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.92,1:41:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这...\NIt...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.63,1:41:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这就好比给个\NIt's like describing a dog
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.16,1:41:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没见过狗的人形容狗\Nto someone who's never seen a dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.26,1:41:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,然后让那人把狗画出来\NAnd then asking them to draw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.24,1:41:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你想让我...形容它\NNow you want me to... describe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.54,1:41:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,然候你记下来 之后呢？\NAnd then you'll write it down, and then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.58,1:41:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 玛丽... - 之后我就能走了吗？\N- Mary-- - You'll let me go?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.48,1:41:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,其实咱们想的一样\NWe all want the same thing here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.95,1:41:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真的\NWe do.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.69,1:41:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们都只想多弄懂一点点\NWe just want to find out even a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.36,1:41:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尔 我最后会怎么样？\NWhat's gonna happen to me, Phil?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.03,1:41:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这不归我管\NThat decision's not up to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.67,1:41:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那...\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.30,1:41:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们能不能就简单聊聊 就咱俩\Nif we could just talk, just you and me,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.21,1:41:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就像...就像普通人那样\Nyou know, just like... just like two regular people.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.18,1:42:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们摊开聊聊 毕竟咱俩都进去过\NWe could unpack some of this, we've both been in there,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.11,1:42:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这样咱...咱们才好在同一个频道上\Nand-and-and get on the same page.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.72,1:42:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,现在到处都在开门\NThere are doors opening everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.42,1:42:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们搞不懂是啥把这些连在一起的\NWe don't know why or what's connecting them.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.69,1:42:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没完没了地出现\NThey sort of keep happening,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.59,1:42:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们完全不知道怎么让它停下来\Nand we don't know how to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.51,1:42:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[山脊公寓]
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.24,1:43:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[《心灵之窗》]
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.22,1:43:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[寻人启事 小凯 阿博]
